data.description: Come see this super cute 3 bedrooms, 1 bathroom home that reminds you of a cottage on a corner lot and enjoy the country style inside and out! Open floor plan in the dining area and living area. Super cute kitchen with lots of cabinets.  There is original wood flooring under the laminated floor in the living area.  Please note the laminated floors in the living area were not done by a professional but are in nice condition.  The bedrooms have the original wood floors still in them for Buyers to view.  Master bedroom currently has a king size bed and still has lots of room for dresser and things.  There is a shop/living quarters right off the back door of the home that used to be used as a beauty salon, it needs renovated but could be used as many things including a mother-in-law home. This shop has a half bath inside and the laundry room is there as well. Cement floor detached Garage with garage door opener.  Roof installed in 2019 on home and on all three buildings. Imagine setting on the front porch drinking coffee and reading your morning paper! Quiet neighborhood and close to schools and not far from Hwy 75.
